Jeenie eliminates language barriers to improve communication between caregivers and their patients, Deaf and hearing persons, international businesses and clients, travelers, and locals.


-- Healthcare Providers --

Better communication results in improved diagnoses and treatment.

The convenience of having an ASL interpreter at your fingertips gives you flexibility in any situation: running errands, ordering at coffee shops and restaurants, socializing with friends and family, engaging with work colleagues, interfacing with landlords and contractors, traveling, and much more.

title: Jeenie: On-Call Language Help

creator: Global Professional Search
descriptionHtml:
Jeenie: LIVE Language Translation
Interpreters On Demand

Jeenie is a mobile platform that connects you to a video or audio call with a LIVE interpreter for on-demand language assistance 24/7. Jeenie provides the better, faster and more affordable video interpreting solution, as well as 3-way calling, so you can hold a conference call with an interpreter on the line.

Jeenie eliminates language barriers to improve communication between caregivers and their patients, Deaf and hearing persons, international businesses and clients, travelers, and locals.


-- Healthcare Providers --

Jeenie connects physicians to video calls with HIPAA-trained medical interpreters so that they can communicate with Limited English Proficiency (LEP) and Deaf patients. Using Jeenie’s 3-way calling feature, caregivers can also conduct telehealth consultations with their LEP patients and an interpreter on the line.

Better communication results in improved diagnoses and treatment.


-- The Deaf Community --

Jeenie is the leading on-demand video interpreting service for the Deaf Community for face-to-face communication with hearing persons. Just open the Jeenie app from your mobile device and, in less than a minute, connect to a qualified ASL interpreter on video.

The convenience of having an ASL interpreter at your fingertips gives you flexibility in any situation: running errands, ordering at coffee shops and restaurants, socializing with friends and family, engaging with work colleagues, interfacing with landlords and contractors, traveling, and much more.


-- Global Businesses --

Do you or your staff engage with international clients or partners who speak other languages? For important, culturally sensitive, face-to-face meetings with clients from other countries, don’t trust the outcome to a machine translation tool: have a live interpreter standing by on video. For conference calls with partners or clients overseas, use Jeenie’s 3-way calling feature to have an interpreter on the line with you.


Everyday Communication in Other Languages
Do you work or interact with people who speak a different language than you do? Planning to travel and don’t speak the language? Using Jeenie is friendlier, faster, and more accurate than trying to translate conversations using computer translation tools.


An Affordable Solution
Jeenie is the most affordable video interpreting service on the market, fastest to set up and the easiest to use. Within less than a minute you will have an interpreter on the line. Individuals can access Jeenie for $1.00/minute, with discount packages available. Enterprise subscription plans are available for healthcare providers and businesses.
